VMware is installed to create and manage virtual machines (VMs) on our computer. It allows us to run multiple operating systems on a single physical machine without interfering with the host operating system.
Go to VMware official website to download https://www.vmware.com/products/desktop-hypervisor/workstation-and-fusion
download file in system.
locate file in system VMware-workstation-full-17.0.0-20800274
Double click on file.
follow the given instruction.
click on install button, installation process stsrted.
click on  finish button.
installation process completed.
if required accept agrement and licences.
